OL,3,CBBC apologises to family of young
OL,4,Cperson over handling of Huw Edwards
OL,5,Ccomplaint
OL,7,FThe has apologised for the way it
OL,8,Fhandled a complaint against its
OL,9,Fpresenter Huw Edwards.
OL,11,FA review found there is a need for
OL,12,F"greater consistency" in how non-
OL,13,Feditorial complaints at the
OL,14,Fcorporation are processed.
OL,16,FA complaint about Edwards was
OL,17,Foriginally made by the family of a
OL,18,Fyoung person to the BBC in May 2023,
OL,19,Fhowever BBC senior leadership was only
OL,20,Finformed of the issue on July 6, the
OL,21,Freview said.
