OL,7,FBBC Group chief operating officer
OL,8,FLeigh Tavaziva said the corporation
OL,9,Fhas since apologised to the
OL,10,Fcomplainant.
OL,12,FThe BBC said it tried to contact the
OL,13,Fcomplainant twice before The Sun
OL,14,Fnewspaper published an exclusive story
OL,15,Fdetailing the allegations that a BBC
OL,16,Fpresenter paid a young person for
OL,17,Fsexually explicit photos.
