OL,7,FEdwards was , and said he was
OL,8,Freceiving in-patient hospital care and
OL,9,Fwas suffering "serious mental health
OL,10,Fissues".
OL,12,FThe Metropolitan Police said at the
OL,13,Ftime the allegations were made that no
OL,14,Fcriminal offence had been committed by
OL,15,Fthe BBC presenter.
