OL,3,CBBC apologises to family of young
OL,4,Cperson over handling of Huw Edwards
OL,5,Ccomplaint
OL,7,FMs Tavaziva said: "Although our
OL,8,Fexisting processes and systems are, on
OL,9,Fthe whole, working effectively, this
OL,10,Freview shows that we need to join them
OL,11,Fup better to ensure no matter how a
OL,12,Fnon-editorial complaint comes into the
OL,13,FBBC it is escalated swiftly, when
OL,14,Fneeded, and dealt with by the right
OL,15,Fpeople.
OL,17,F"Where the review identifies process
OL,18,Fimprovements we accept those in full,
OL,19,Fand we are delivering on an action
OL,20,Fplan with a number of enhancements
OL,21,Falready in place.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G4/10
