OL,7,F"The report identifies specific
OL,8,Fprocess shortcomings in the presenter
OL,9,Fcase. The initial complaint in this
OL,10,Fcase was not escalated quickly enough
OL,11,Fto senior management and we have
OL,12,Fapologised to the complainant for
OL,13,Fthis."
OL,15,FBBC director-general Tim Davie ordered
OL,16,Fa review to "assess how some
OL,17,Fcomplaints are red-flagged up the
OL,18,Forganisation", in the wake of the
OL,19,Fallegations last year.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G5/10
