OL,5,Ccomplaint
OL,7,FHe also ordered an additional
OL,8,F"factfinding investigation".
OL,10,FThe review, led by Ms Tavaziva and
OL,11,Fcarried out by Deloitte, highlights
OL,12,Ffailures in the complaints process,
OL,13,Fsaying that the initial complaint
OL,14,Fabout Edwards was not logged on the
OL,15,Frelevant case management system so
OL,16,Fcould not be seen by senior figures.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G6/10
