OL,3,CBBC apologises to family of young
OL,4,Cperson over handling of Huw Edwards
OL,5,Ccomplaint
OL,7,FThere was also no documented process
OL,8,Ffor contact and follow-ups with the
OL,9,Fcomplainant, so when attempts to make
OL,10,Fcontact were unsuccessful, the course
OL,11,Fof action was not clear.
OL,13,FAdditionally, the report flagged that
OL,14,Fsome employees interviewed said they
OL,15,Fwould feel nervous about raising a
OL,16,Fcomplaint with the BBC, particularly
OL,17,Fif it was about a more senior member
OL,18,Fof staff or a high profile figure.
OL,1,Wz5~k4~k7}hw1 ~k4~sj5j5~s1 G     G7/10
